                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10267" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1519</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">297 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">因为米粉，所以小米：小米顾客关系跃迁之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Because of Mi Fans, There is Xiaomi: The Evolution of Xiaomi’s Customer Relationships</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李念，李艳君，李萌妹，费玉琪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李念</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米科技有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顾客关系；顾客信息；顾客资源；顾客资产；顾客资本</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Customer Relationship; Customer Information; Customer Resources; Customer Assets; Customer Capital</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例聚焦小米公司自2010年创立以来的战略演进与用户关系建设历程。小米以“因为米粉，所以小米”为理念，逐步实现了从积累用户信息、整合用户资源、沉淀用户资产到运营顾客资本的价值跃迁。在发展路径上，小米以智能手机为起点，通过生态链构建和智能汽车跨界，持续拓展用户共创边界。通过系统分析这一完整过程，启发学员深化对顾客关系的认知与探究，理解顾客资本在企业战略转型中的核心价值。案例着重阐释小米如何通过社区运营、用户共创和生态协同，将用户深度参与转化为可持续竞争优势。这一实践表明，企业不仅需要系统掌握顾客关系从初级到高级的形态演进规律，更应在实际运营中重视顾客资本的战略性积累与转化。案例通过展现“与用户交朋友”理念的实践历程，帮助学员增强对客户关系生命周期等理论的理解与应用，培养用户导向的创业思维，为构建长期、可信、共生的新型用户关系提供实践参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study focuses on the strategic evolution and user relationship development of Xiaomi since its establishment in 2010. Guided by the philosophy “because of Mi fans, so there is Xiaomi”, Xiaomi has systematically progressed through four distinct stages of customer value development: from data collection and resource integration to asset cultivation and ultimately, capital mobilization. In terms of its development path, Xiaomi started with smartphones, expanded through ecosystem building, and ventured into smart electric vehicles, continuously extending the boundaries of user co-creation. By systematically analyzing this comprehensive process, the case aims to inspire learners to deepen their understanding of customer relationships and explore the core value of customer capital in corporate strategic transformation. It elaborates on how Xiaomi leverages community operations, user co-creation, and ecosystem collaboration to translate deep user engagement into sustainable competitive advantages. This practice demonstrates that enterprises must not only grasp the evolutionary patterns of customer relationships from the nascent stage to advanced stages but also prioritize the strategic accumulation and transformation of customer capital in actual operations. By illustrating the implementation path of the “making friends with customers” concept, the case helps learners enhance their comprehension and application of theories such as the customer relationship life cycle, fosters a user-oriented entrepreneurial mindset, and provides practical insights for building long-term, trustworthy, and symbiotic modern user relationships.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《客户关系管理》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">客户生命周期理论；顾客信息；顾客资源；顾客资产；顾客资本；客户关系管理；资源基础理论；顾客资产管理理论；动态能力理论；价值共创理论；期望确认理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
